      <body>
        <div>
            <pb facs="#TL-0422.jpg" n="part3_p030.jpg" xml:id="img_0030" corresp="https://id.acdh.oeaw.ac.at/tillich-lectures/part3_p030.jpg"/>
            
            <p facs="#facs_30_tr_1">
               <lb facs="#facs_30_tr_1_tl_1" n="N001"/>vous avez
               <lb facs="#facs_30_tr_1_tl_2" n="N002"/>-117-
               <lb facs="#facs_30_tr_1_tl_3" n="N003"/>This is not even true of their own school, where they are first of all administrators and then
               <lb facs="#facs_30_tr_1_tl_4" n="N004"/>educational ideas. (some daughter) But it is
               <lb facs="#facs_30_tr_1_tl_5" n="N005"/>SOMEtimes one of them has also some
               <lb facs="#facs_30_tr_1_tl_6" n="N006"/>certainly NOT true, in no way true, of the general situation of education in this country. There
               <lb facs="#facs_30_tr_1_tl_7" n="N007"/>are other powers much more important, [just] as in Europe before the totalitarian movements came.
               <lb facs="#facs_30_tr_1_tl_8" n="N008"/>And the first is the [home] : the [home] was able to give bidden resistance—hidden; open was
               <lb facs="#facs_30_tr_1_tl_9" n="N009"/>impossible—to its own system, even in totalitarian systems. Not open—because the children would
            </p>
            <p facs="#facs_30_tr_3">
               <lb facs="#facs_30_tr_3_tl_1" n="N001"/>go to the next Gauleiter and would accuse their parents, under Nazism; but bidden, by the very
               <lb facs="#facs_30_tr_3_tl_2" n="N002"/>existence of the [home], by the reality, which is always reality of introduction, and the introduction
               <lb facs="#facs_30_tr_3_tl_3" n="N003"/>into the [home] Aarts with birth and is therefore the most important one.
               <lb facs="#facs_30_tr_3_tl_4" n="N004"/>Then there are also in this country other powers—of course the churches —and the
               <lb facs="#facs_30_tr_3_tl_5" n="N005"/>representatives of the political ideas about which fight is going on. And then very important—and
               <lb facs="#facs_30_tr_3_tl_6" n="N006"/>that, all teachers should know—the gang, in the largest sense of the word. I have been aducated
               <lb facs="#facs_30_tr_3_tl_7" n="N007"/>in Very important respects by a Christian fraternity to which I belonged in Germany—for a
            </p>
            <p facs="#facs_30_tr_2">
               <lb facs="#facs_30_tr_2_tl_1" n="N001"/>life¬time, that is, of course, but decisively for four or five years. And there, those plus¬
               <lb facs="#facs_30_tr_2_tl_2" n="N002"/>were a little bit older, one or two years older, were the REAL authorities-we didn't care very much
               <lb facs="#facs_30_tr_2_tl_3" n="N003"/>about the professors in Iomparison with the older students—and I think you do the same!
               <lb facs="#facs_30_tr_2_tl_4" n="N004"/>Now here you have a very large concept of education, and the TITLE ("educators")
               <lb facs="#facs_30_tr_2_tl_5" n="N005"/>should be applied to all of them. Now a little more about this Thursday.
               <lb facs="#facs_30_tr_2_tl_6" n="N006"/>de mon ami
               <lb facs="#facs_30_tr_2_tl_7" n="N007"/>Monsieur, que je mʼadresse à lʼannée
               <lb facs="#facs_30_tr_2_tl_8" n="N008"/>Monsieur
               <lb facs="#facs_30_tr_2_tl_9" n="N009"/>cette
               <lb facs="#facs_30_tr_2_tl_10" n="N010"/>ou vous intérieurez
               <lb facs="#facs_30_tr_2_tl_11" n="N011"/>G.C.F.P.
            </p>
            
